# Claude Harness Kit — repository .gitignore (public)
#
# This kit repo contains only documentation, rules, skills, and CI/PR
# templates — so this file mostly keeps OS/editor junk and local-only state
# out of the published history. Note: `.claude/` (rules & skills) IS part of
# the kit and must stay tracked — no pattern here may match it.

# ── OS junk ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
._*
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ── Editors / IDEs ───────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Stray tool artifacts ─────────────────────────────────
.Rhistory
*.log

# ── Claude Code local state (machine-local, never publish) ──
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude
.gitignore

# ── Build/dependency dirs (if examples or tooling are ever added) ──
node_modules/
target/
dist/

# ── Packaging artifacts ──────────────────────────────────
*.zip
